          = image_tag 'about_img1.jpg'
.photo-section data-background-image="assets/services_img.jpg"
  .text-content.white-font
    .container
      .row
        .col-lg-6.col-md-8.col-sm-12   
          h2
            | Eazy management
          p 
            strong.color
              | Room Passport     
            | team performs a wide range of companies office management services.  
