    .row.services-items
      div class="col-xl-3 col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-12 services-content row-one"
        .line.line-one
        .icon
          i.fa.fa-building
        .line.line-two
        .item
          .item-title Quick company registration
          .item-text 
            | We appreciate your time and help you to register your company in one step. 
            | The person who create the company automatically get all company owners rights.              
      div class="col-xl-3 col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-12 services-content row-one"
        .line.line-one
        .icon
          i.fa.fa-address-card
        .line.line-two
        .item
          .item-title Communication between users
          .item-text
            | User communication is a core aspect of our bisness. 
            | We provide clear task reporting system, which helps company owners and employees to be informed all the time.
      div class="col-xl-3 col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-12 services-content row-one"
        .line.line-one
        .icon
          i.fa.fa-inbox
        .line.line-two
        .item
          .item-title User-friendly interface
          .item-text
            | Our software interface is really easy to understand. We anticipate what users might need to do and ensure 
              | that interface elements are easy to access, understand, and use.
      div class="col-xl-3 col-lg-3 col-md-6 col-sm-6 col-12 services-content row-one"
        .line.line-one
        .icon
